from the East Sea Team.

381
00:21:30,370 --> 00:21:32,400
Please deliver it as soon as possible.

382
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:36,310
[Cai Xiaoqian, alias Zheng,
Secretary of CPC Taiwan Work Committee]

383
00:21:32,890 --> 00:21:33,640
So quick?

384
00:21:34,770 --> 00:21:36,170
We just met a few days ago.

385
00:21:36,850 --> 00:21:38,650
The East Sea Team is impressive.

386
00:21:39,950 --> 00:21:42,350
I'm only responsible
for a small part of it,

387
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,100
just running errands.

388
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:44,820
Mrs. Chen.

389
00:21:46,460 --> 00:21:47,980
You don't look well.

390
00:21:49,030 --> 00:21:50,160
Is something wrong?

391
00:21:51,360 --> 00:21:53,820
There was a small incident just now,

392
00:21:53,970 --> 00:21:54,930
but it's fine.

393
00:21:55,020 --> 00:21:56,020
It's over now.

394
00:21:56,210 --> 00:21:58,340
I'll have to trouble you with the rest.

395
00:21:58,740 --> 00:22:00,550
We'll do our best to help you
deliver the intelligence.

396
00:22:00,550 --> 00:22:01,980
That's our mission.

397
00:22:02,610 --> 00:22:04,810
We'll be accountable to our superiors.

398
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:05,980
Mrs. Chen.

399
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:08,160
Even if it's not a mission,

400
00:22:08,980 --> 00:22:11,920
just let me know if you need anything.

401
00:22:13,230 --> 00:22:14,160
You're too kind.

402
00:22:17,150 --> 00:22:18,420
The line is fixed?

403
00:22:22,610 --> 00:22:24,210
This is Hongxiang Silk Shop.

404
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:25,890
Is this Mrs. Chen's residence?

405
00:22:25,890 --> 00:22:26,700
She's not home.

406
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:28,030
What can I help you with?

407
00:22:29,510 --> 00:22:31,290
The fabric Madam ordered from our shop
has arrived.

408
00:22:31,290 --> 00:22:32,420
Please let her know.

409
00:22:33,770 --> 00:22:35,500
I'll tell her when she returns.

410
00:22:58,630 --> 00:22:59,590
I'm back.

411
00:23:00,150 --> 00:23:02,340
Mom, you're back.

412
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,360
What happened?

413
00:23:03,390 --> 00:23:05,520
Where have you been all night?

414
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:06,880
I was so worried!

415
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,880
-Sit down.
-Sorry for worrying you.

416
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:11,420
Mom, what happened?

417
00:23:11,700 --> 00:23:13,380
You didn't come home all night yesterday.

418
00:23:13,380 --> 00:23:14,550
I was so worried!

419
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:17,500
I went out shopping,

420
00:23:18,110 --> 00:23:19,010
and while I was shopping,

421
00:23:19,010 --> 00:23:20,880
I ran into people from the BIS.

422
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,460
They mistook me for a spy

423
00:23:22,460 --> 00:23:23,510
and arrested me.

424
00:23:24,330 --> 00:23:25,630
After all that trouble,

425
00:23:25,630 --> 00:23:27,270
it turned out they just wanted some money,

426
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,110
you know?

427
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:30,140
Then, I told them

428
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,880
that my son-in-law

429
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:34,160
is Wang Changcheng
from the Provincial Police Department.

430
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,320
They knew you

431
00:23:35,450 --> 00:23:37,770
and said I needed to call and verify.

432
00:23:38,360 --> 00:23:39,140
Changcheng.

433
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:42,080
Were you not at work yesterday?

434
00:23:42,110 --> 00:23:44,010
I was on field duty last night,

435
00:23:44,010 --> 00:23:45,010
not at the office.

436
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:47,290
Alas!

437
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:49,910
Then, why was no one
answering the phone at home?

438
00:23:49,910 --> 00:23:51,620
The home phone was broken yesterday.

439
00:23:51,620 --> 00:23:53,350
It was only fixed this morning.

440
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:55,020
What a coincidence.

441
00:23:55,020 --> 00:23:57,390
Mom, they didn't hurt you,

442
00:23:57,620 --> 00:23:58,510
did they?

443
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:01,270
It was just a matter of

444
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:02,930
solving the problem with money.

445
00:24:02,930 --> 00:24:04,270
Changcheng has quite a reputation.

446
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:06,110
When I mentioned his name,

447
00:24:06,140 --> 00:24:07,270
they all knew who he was

448
00:24:07,270 --> 00:24:08,770
and even gave me food.

449
00:24:09,460 --> 00:24:11,560
What's important is you're back safely.

450
00:24:11,560 --> 00:24:12,720
If anything had happened to you,

451
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:14,620
how would I explain to my siblings?

452
00:24:14,620 --> 00:24:16,740
At least those brats had some conscience,

453
00:24:16,740 --> 00:24:19,200
otherwise I wouldn't
let them off so easily!

454
00:24:19,280 --> 00:24:20,140
By the way, Mom,

455
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:22,590
where exactly were you detained?

456
00:24:22,790 --> 00:24:24,610
I asked several colleagues at the BIS,

457
00:24:24,610 --> 00:24:25,510
but none of them knew.

458
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:26,550
About that detention place,

459
00:24:26,550 --> 00:24:28,410
I'm not sure where it was, either.

460
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,660
The moment I woke up today,

461
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:32,270
they released me.

462
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:35,400
How can they just arrest people at will?

463
00:24:35,460 --> 00:24:36,660
Extorting money
from ordinary people all day—

464
00:24:36,660 --> 00:24:38,320
what kind of behavior is that?

465
00:24:39,170 --> 00:24:40,930
Ju, I'm so sorry

466
00:24:41,390 --> 00:24:43,120
for causing you so much trouble

467
00:24:43,170 --> 00:24:44,360
and making you worried

468
00:24:44,360 --> 00:24:45,290
and concerned.

469
00:24:45,460 --> 00:24:46,660
I apologize to you.

470
00:24:46,660 --> 00:24:48,190
Please don't say that, Mom.

471
00:24:49,910 --> 00:24:51,010
It's getting late.

472
00:24:51,010 --> 00:24:52,620
I need to go to work.
You two can go on chatting.

473
00:24:52,620 --> 00:24:53,260
Alright.

474
00:24:58,380 --> 00:24:59,240
By the way, Mom,

475
00:24:59,420 --> 00:25:02,170
did you order any fabric from

476
00:25:02,190 --> 00:25:03,790
Hongxiang Silk Shop before?

477
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:04,740
No, I didn't.

478
00:25:05,050 --> 00:25:06,010
That's strange.

479
00:25:06,010 --> 00:25:07,290
Someone called today saying

480
00:25:07,290 --> 00:25:09,020
your fabric order has arrived.

481
00:25:12,890 --> 00:25:14,090
Oh! Yes, yes!

482
00:25:14,230 --> 00:25:15,400
I did order it.

483
00:25:16,110 --> 00:25:18,460
I... It is quite hot in Hong Kong,

484
00:25:18,510 --> 00:25:19,830
but it's cold in Taipei.

485
00:25:19,830 --> 00:25:21,720
So I wanted to get some more clothes made.

486
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,630
I was so tired

487
00:25:22,660 --> 00:25:24,400
that I forgot it.

488
00:25:24,430 --> 00:25:25,720
Yes, I did order it.

489
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:27,460
It's fine, Mom.
Don't forget to pick it up.

490
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:28,110
I'm leaving now.

491
00:25:28,110 --> 00:25:29,200
Alright.

492
00:25:30,740 --> 00:25:31,830
Mom, what would you like to eat?

493
00:25:31,830 --> 00:25:32,650
I'll make it for you now.

494
00:25:32,650 --> 00:25:33,790
No need, Ju.

495
00:25:33,980 --> 00:25:36,260
All I want now is to get some sleep.

496
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:37,690
I'm so tired!

497
00:25:38,430 --> 00:25:39,250
Ju.

498
00:25:40,120 --> 00:25:41,650
I want to ask you something.

499
00:25:41,700 --> 00:25:43,630
Since I've been staying at your home,

500
00:25:43,630 --> 00:25:45,430
I've caused you so much trouble.

501
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:47,430
Has Changcheng been displeased about it?

502
00:25:47,430 --> 00:25:48,620
Not at all, Mom.

503
00:25:49,270 --> 00:25:50,530
You're overthinking.

504
00:25:50,590 --> 00:25:51,850
You've come to help us,

505
00:25:52,090 --> 00:25:53,620
contributing to our household expenses

506
00:25:53,620 --> 00:25:55,200
and helping us taking care of the baby.

507
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:56,490
You've saved us a lot of worry.

508
00:25:56,490 --> 00:25:57,820
We couldn't be happier!

509
00:25:57,840 --> 00:25:59,040
Then, I can rest easy.

510
00:25:59,570 --> 00:26:00,770
I'll go get some rest.

511
00:28:10,700 --> 00:28:13,810
