512
00:28:17,110 --> 00:28:17,560
Madam.

513
00:28:17,890 --> 00:28:19,350
What would you like to buy?

514
00:28:19,850 --> 00:28:21,580
I'd like to look at some fabric.

515
00:28:21,590 --> 00:28:22,450
Fabric, right?

516
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:23,880
Our shop

517
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,390
just received a new batch of fine fabrics.

518
00:28:25,390 --> 00:28:26,340
I guarantee you'll like them.

519
00:28:26,340 --> 00:28:26,730
Good.

520
00:28:26,770 --> 00:28:27,770
This way, please.

521
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:31,410
Look. This is

522
00:28:31,430 --> 00:28:33,880
the fabric that arrived from the West
a few days ago.

523
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:35,740
It was just made into a cheongsam.

524
00:28:35,950 --> 00:28:37,480
See how bright the color is.

525
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:38,870
The material is excellent too.

526
00:28:38,870 --> 00:28:39,920
Yes, and this one too.

527
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:40,960
You can feel it.

528
00:28:41,550 --> 00:28:42,380
This fabric.

529
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,810
Feels nice, doesn't it?

530
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:46,770
Where is this from?

531
00:28:46,770 --> 00:28:48,740
This one is from Southeast Asia.

532
00:28:48,760 --> 00:28:49,510
You can take a look at it too.

533
00:28:49,510 --> 00:28:50,050
Hello.

534
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,210
Sir.

535
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:52,700
You called to inform me

536
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:54,240
that Mrs. Chen's fabric order has arrived.

537
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,440
I'm here to pick it up.

538
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:57,950
Madam, please continue browsing here.

539
00:28:58,420 --> 00:29:00,220
