548
00:29:22,550 --> 00:29:23,480
so I came over.

549
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:27,290
I just came to look at some fabric.

550
00:29:27,290 --> 00:29:28,480
Just in case.

551
00:29:29,270 --> 00:29:30,010
Alright.

552
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:34,660
