553
00:29:35,310 --> 00:29:36,370
Just a moment, sir.

554
00:29:45,550 --> 00:29:48,420
Look at you, coming to take care of me
while you're working.

555
00:29:48,420 --> 00:29:49,960
I'm really causing you trouble.

556
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:50,700
It's no trouble, Mom.

557
00:29:50,700 --> 00:29:51,680
I'll keep you company for a while.

558
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:52,520
We're family.

559
00:29:56,370 --> 00:29:57,090
Found it!

560
00:29:57,620 --> 00:29:58,420
It's this one.

561
00:30:01,860 --> 00:30:05,470
Yes, this fabric was delivered
from the mainland a few days ago.

562
00:30:05,550 --> 00:30:06,770
It's so smooth.

563
00:30:07,010 --> 00:30:08,010
And the color is elegant.

564
00:30:08,010 --> 00:30:09,570
It's just that it's a bit expensive.

565
00:30:09,570 --> 00:30:11,100
You really have good taste.

566
00:30:11,550 --> 00:30:12,050
Here.

567
00:30:13,630 --> 00:30:16,350
Mom, let me call a rickshaw for you.

568
00:30:16,370 --> 00:30:17,700
I'm running out of time.

569
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:19,860
Changcheng, no need.

570
00:30:20,050 --> 00:30:22,160
I want to look around a bit more.

571
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,250
You should hurry to work.

572
00:30:23,250 --> 00:30:24,250
Don't be late!

573
00:30:24,460 --> 00:30:25,460
Alright, then.

574
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:26,340
I'm off to work.

575
00:30:26,410 --> 00:30:26,820
Okay.

576
00:30:27,650 --> 00:30:29,460
Madam, let's continue looking over here.

577
00:30:29,460 --> 00:30:29,790
Alright.

578
00:30:29,790 --> 00:30:30,700
There are two more kinds of fabric here

579
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:31,550
that I haven't shown you yet.

580
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:33,350
They've also arrived recently.

581
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:36,500
Should be this…

582
00:30:59,010 --> 00:30:59,700
Thank you.

583
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,380
It was due to my poor arrangement.

584
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:04,840
I'm sorry you had to suffer.

585
00:31:04,840 --> 00:31:05,440
Not at all.

586
00:31:06,180 --> 00:31:07,640
Thank you for rescuing me.

587
00:31:08,010 --> 00:31:09,570
And I must thank Adjutant Nie

588
00:31:09,570 --> 00:31:12,370
for covering up the matter
at Hongxiang Silk Shop.

589
00:31:12,980 --> 00:31:14,380
It was what we ought to do.

590
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:20,250
Since he used the clerk's phone call
as an excuse,

591
00:31:20,290 --> 00:31:22,150
we couldn't leave any loose ends.

592
00:31:23,350 --> 00:31:25,330
The film I gave you last time
was destroyed, right?

593
00:31:25,330 --> 00:31:26,650
I brought you a backup.

594
00:31:26,690 --> 00:31:27,300
No need.

595
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,680
I've sent it out.

596
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:33,700
You've sent it out?

597
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:34,680
Yes.

598
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:38,610
In such a dangerous situation,

599
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:41,360
why didn't you
destroy the film right away?

600
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,840
I instructed you to do so.

601
00:31:43,700 --> 00:31:45,830
It's not easy to gather intelligence.

602
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:47,480
If it could be preserved,

603
00:31:47,890 --> 00:31:49,890
shouldn't we try our best to keep it?

604
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:57,460
Before you came to Taiwan,

605
00:31:58,630 --> 00:32:00,000
didn't Wan tell you?

606
00:32:01,010 --> 00:32:03,600
Safety comes first in clandestine work.

607
00:32:04,980 --> 00:32:07,980
You will be safe only after
the evidence is destroyed.

608
00:32:08,740 --> 00:32:12,140
Only then will the comrades
of the intelligence line be safe.

609
00:32:12,310 --> 00:32:15,710
But we should handle things
according to the circumstances.

610
00:32:16,050 --> 00:32:17,190
I was told about

611
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:19,080
the time sensitivity of this intelligence.

612
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:20,650
If I didn't send it out,

613
00:32:20,890 --> 00:32:22,900
when would it ever be delivered?

614
00:32:22,930 --> 00:32:24,560
Besides, I didn't know there was a backup!

615
00:32:24,560 --> 00:32:26,290
It's such important material.

616
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:27,900
Why did you act on your own

617
00:32:28,320 --> 00:32:29,450
and disobey orders?

618
00:32:34,330 --> 00:32:36,330
Even if you managed to save the film,

619
00:32:36,700 --> 00:32:38,380
how could you go to the rendezvous

620
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:39,980
right after leaving the BIS?

621
00:32:40,380 --> 00:32:41,830
Are you sure you weren't followed?

622
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:43,090
I checked repeatedly.

623
00:32:43,610 --> 00:32:45,940
There were absolutely no security risks.

624
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,110
As a courier,

625
00:32:47,460 --> 00:32:49,300
my primary duty is
to deliver intelligence.

626
00:32:49,300 --> 00:32:51,100
Isn't that the right thing to do?

627
00:32:53,090 --> 00:32:55,220
I just said safety is the top priority.

628
00:32:55,390 --> 00:32:56,750
Delivering intelligence comes second.

629
00:32:56,750 --> 00:32:58,010
Don't you understand?

630
00:33:19,630 --> 00:33:20,630
Comrade Zhu Feng,

631
00:33:21,660 --> 00:33:23,120
have you considered this?

632
00:33:23,620 --> 00:33:26,080
Once the film falls into
the hands of the BIS,

633
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:27,640
your life will be in danger.

634
00:33:28,700 --> 00:33:30,750
The Taiwan Work Committee
will have to withdraw,

635
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:32,750
and your family will be implicated.

636
00:33:32,760 --> 00:33:35,290
The East Sea Team will be
completely exposed.

637
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:37,890
Most importantly,

638
00:33:38,690 --> 00:33:40,340
our superior will lose

639
00:33:40,370 --> 00:33:44,170
the most crucial intelligence source
from the Ministry of Defense.

640
00:33:46,980 --> 00:33:48,010
From now on,

641
00:33:48,230 --> 00:33:50,160
we'll suspend all communication.

642
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:52,630
I need to think about our next steps

643
00:33:53,010 --> 00:33:53,860
before contacting you again.

644
00:33:53,860 --> 00:33:54,720
Comrade Wu Shi,

645
00:33:55,090 --> 00:33:56,690
where will we meet next time?

646
00:33:57,170 --> 00:33:58,900
Go back and get some rest first.

647
00:33:59,460 --> 00:34:00,660
Be sure to stay safe.

648
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:01,820
Comrade Wu Shi.

649
00:34:03,830 --> 00:34:04,850
I didn't come to Taiwan

650
00:34:04,850 --> 00:34:05,910
to take a vacation.

651
00:34:07,610 --> 00:34:08,699
Originally,

652
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:12,150
someone else was supposed
to carry out this mission.

653
00:34:12,150 --> 00:34:13,190
But due to an unexpected incident,

654
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,150
I came instead.

655
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:17,179
I know I made a mistake.

656
00:34:18,290 --> 00:34:20,350
But this is my first time as a courier.

657
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:24,090
Shouldn't you give me another chance?

658
00:34:25,090 --> 00:34:27,489
My previous courier was Taiwanese.

659
00:34:28,730 --> 00:34:31,330
He had been in the revolution
for over a decade.

660
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:33,690
He was reliable and competent

661
00:34:33,690 --> 00:34:35,090
and never made a mistake,

662
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:37,340
yet I still had to watch him

663
00:34:37,340 --> 00:34:38,690
die right in front of me.

664
00:34:40,520 --> 00:34:41,830
In our line of work,

665
00:34:42,409 --> 00:34:44,340
there often isn't a second chance.

666
00:34:47,190 --> 00:34:49,690
You think I'm worried about
the safety of the intelligence.

667
00:34:49,690 --> 00:34:50,360
Wrong!

668
00:34:51,449 --> 00:34:53,460
I just don't want my courier

669
00:34:54,510 --> 00:34:55,840
to be sacrificed again.

670
00:35:02,770 --> 00:35:03,570
I understand.

671
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:08,650
I know I made a mistake.

672
00:35:10,860 --> 00:35:11,920
Wait for my notice.

673
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:13,380
Before that,

674
00:35:15,310 --> 00:35:16,570
don't take any action.

675
00:35:36,410 --> 00:35:37,410
Comrade Zhu Feng,

676
00:35:38,230 --> 00:35:39,690
have you considered this?

677
00:35:40,210 --> 00:35:42,670
Once the film falls into
the hands of the BIS,

678
00:35:42,680 --> 00:35:44,210
your life will be in danger.

679
00:35:45,280 --> 00:35:47,340
The Taiwan Work Committee
will have to withdraw,

680
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:49,340
and your family will be implicated.

681
00:35:59,220 --> 00:36:00,340
Mom, you're back.

682
00:36:05,010 --> 00:36:06,010
Did you make this?

683
00:36:07,010 --> 00:36:08,940
It's the Ningbo rice cake you love,

684
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,840
along with many other Ningbo dishes.

685
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:13,100
Thank you for coming to Taiwan to help us.

686
00:36:14,420 --> 00:36:15,480
I should thank you.

687
00:36:16,130 --> 00:36:17,630
What are you thanking us for?

688
00:36:17,630 --> 00:36:19,840
You're the one helping Changcheng
make money in business.

689
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:21,370
We're the ones benefiting.

690
00:36:23,010 --> 00:36:24,550
Changcheng, serve the yellow croaker.

691
00:36:24,550 --> 00:36:25,290
Right away.

692
00:36:25,310 --> 00:36:26,290
No need.

693
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:27,900
I'm a bit tired now.

694
00:36:27,900 --> 00:36:29,430
I'd like to rest for a while.

695
00:36:30,090 --> 00:36:31,220
You go ahead and eat.

696
00:36:39,180 --> 00:36:40,440
What's wrong with Mom?

697
00:36:42,170 --> 00:36:43,570
Mom says she's a bit tired

698
00:36:43,750 --> 00:36:44,870
and wants to rest.

699
00:37:34,130 --> 00:37:35,960
Yiliang still hasn't shown up.

700
00:37:37,860 --> 00:37:39,660
Could something have happened?

701
00:37:39,810 --> 00:37:43,460
[Chen Zemin, Deputy Secretary
of CPC Keelung Work Committee]

702
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:42,840
Rebuilding the communication line
in one week

703
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:44,400
is indeed a daunting task.

704
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:48,180
If he doesn't arrive before dark,

705
00:37:48,810 --> 00:37:50,310
I'll go to Keelung myself.

706
00:37:55,570 --> 00:37:57,300
I guess that's our only option.

707
00:38:00,520 --> 00:38:01,780
Be careful on your way.

708
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:05,390
Don't worry, Zheng. I have experience.

709
00:38:05,780 --> 00:38:07,150
If anything happens,

710
00:38:07,150 --> 00:38:09,210
contact the local liaison directly.

711
00:38:11,970 --> 00:38:12,670
Yiliang.

712
00:38:13,650 --> 00:38:14,550
Why are you so late?

713
00:38:14,550 --> 00:38:15,840
Did anything happen on your way here?

714
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:16,360
What's wrong?

715
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:17,520
I was stopped at a checkpoint.

716
00:38:17,520 --> 00:38:18,980
It's fine. I can handle it.

717
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:20,840
The new communication station
is ready to use.

718
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:21,800
The intelligence.

719
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,450
Hurry.

720
00:38:25,960 --> 00:38:27,220
Good that you're safe.

721
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:33,040
The film is inside.

722
00:38:33,510 --> 00:38:34,050
Here.

723
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:36,760
Alright, I'll leave, then.

724
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:37,620
Wait, Yiliang.

725
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:39,430
You haven't eaten anything, have you?

726
00:38:39,430 --> 00:38:40,570
Haven't seen you for a week.

727
00:38:40,570 --> 00:38:41,560
You look exhausted.

728
00:38:41,560 --> 00:38:42,360
Wait a moment.

729
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,260
Take this.

730
00:38:49,070 --> 00:38:49,710
Thanks.

731
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:01,940
Zheng.

732
00:39:03,420 --> 00:39:05,140
Did you know Zhang Hao's real name

733
00:39:05,140 --> 00:39:06,390
was Lin Yiwei?

734
00:39:07,600 --> 00:39:09,400
Yiliang is his younger brother.

735
00:39:13,540 --> 00:39:15,980
On December 10, 1949,

736
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:19,600
Chiang Kai-shek hastily evacuated
from Chengdu.

737
00:39:19,610 --> 00:39:23,560
He flew directly to Taiwan
on his private plane, the "Zhongmei."

738
00:39:23,630 --> 00:39:25,410
Now broadcasting the news.

739
00:39:25,630 --> 00:39:28,860
On the afternoon of November 30, 1949,

740
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:32,850
the PLA, advancing toward Chongqing

741
00:39:33,240 --> 00:39:36,360
after occupying Jiangjin,

742
00:39:36,380 --> 00:39:38,500
Shunjiangchang, Yudong Town,

743
00:39:38,520 --> 00:39:40,980
Nanwenquan and Mudong Town
on the south bank of the Yangtze River,

744
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:44,460
crossed the Yangtze River
from these places

745
00:39:44,790 --> 00:39:47,190
and liberated Chongqing in the afternoon.

746
00:39:54,130 --> 00:39:55,060
Keep listening.

747
00:39:59,340 --> 00:40:01,470
On the eve of Chongqing's liberation,

748
00:40:01,610 --> 00:40:04,280
the remnants of the Kuomintang
scrambled to escape

749
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:05,420
in disarray.

750
00:40:05,870 --> 00:40:08,410
On the morning of the 30th,
Chiang Kai-shek

751
00:40:08,430 --> 00:40:10,460
fled in panic to Chengdu.

752
00:40:10,730 --> 00:40:14,440
Yan Xishan and Zhang Qun had already

753
00:40:14,470 --> 00:40:16,010
fled to Chengdu on the 28th.

754
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:18,110
The collapse of the Southwest defense line

755
00:40:18,110 --> 00:40:20,130
-completely crushed Chiang Kai-shek's
-Sir.

756
00:40:20,130 --> 00:40:22,270
-dream of a decisive battle in Sichuan.
-On the meeting just now,

757
00:40:22,270 --> 00:40:25,000
what did they say
about Chongqing's liberation ?

758
00:40:25,760 --> 00:40:27,820
Go tune in to the Central News Agency.

759
00:40:34,300 --> 00:40:37,020
To preserve its strength
and fight elsewhere,

760
00:40:37,050 --> 00:40:38,530
the Nationalist Army

761
00:40:38,810 --> 00:40:41,010
voluntarily withdrew from Chongqing.

762
00:40:41,710 --> 00:40:45,080
President Chiang,
reluctant to leave the wartime capital,

763
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:47,740
held out until the very last moment.

764
00:40:48,230 --> 00:40:51,100
Only on December 1st

765
00:40:51,130 --> 00:40:54,480
did he go to Chengdu
to continue commanding.

766
00:40:56,160 --> 00:41:00,780
Taichung area:
cloudy with scattered showers,

767
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:04,350
15 to 28 degrees.

768
00:41:04,380 --> 00:41:06,380
Having lost Chongqing as a barrier,

769
00:41:06,570 --> 00:41:08,810
Chiang Kai-shek actually wants to fight

770
00:41:08,810 --> 00:41:11,230
a decisive battle with the PLA
in the western Sichuan plain.

771
00:41:11,230 --> 00:41:12,960
The troops of the Southwest Office,

772
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:15,090
from Hu Zongnan down to Sun Yuanliang,

773
00:41:15,600 --> 00:41:17,850
are all clustered together.

774
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:22,080
Which one of them has the determination
to fight to the death?

775
00:41:22,630 --> 00:41:25,360
How can they fight a decisive battle
with the PLA?

776
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:29,880
The liberation of Chengdu
is just a matter of time.

777
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:32,150
Sir, you previously worked
as an interpreter for the White Group

778
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:33,340
and suffered so much hardship.

779
00:41:33,340 --> 00:41:35,590
Now it all seems worthwhile.

780
00:41:36,180 --> 00:41:37,380
Let me use tea instead of wine

781
00:41:37,380 --> 00:41:38,150
to toast you

782
00:41:38,340 --> 00:41:39,270
in celebration.

783
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:41,490
Why use tea instead of wine?

784
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:46,170
Get some wine. Let's have a drink.

785
00:41:46,170 --> 00:41:47,000
In the office?

786
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,380
This is the office.

787
00:41:53,290 --> 00:41:54,090
That's not appropriate, is it?

788
00:41:54,090 --> 00:41:54,950
I want to drink.

789
00:41:55,340 --> 00:41:56,470
You should have one.

790
00:41:56,780 --> 00:41:58,210
I'll drink with you tonight
when we get back.

791
00:41:58,210 --> 00:41:59,070
I want to drink.

792
00:41:59,260 --> 00:42:00,390
We're in the office. If someone sees…

793
00:42:00,390 --> 00:42:01,340
I want to drink.

794
00:42:03,840 --> 00:42:05,240
Can't I drown my sorrows?

795
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,250
Drowning your sorrows?

796
00:42:08,650 --> 00:42:09,150
Fine.

797
00:42:22,410 --> 00:42:23,940
I'll go take a shower first.

798
00:42:28,060 --> 00:42:28,860
Adjutant Nie.

799
00:42:29,130 --> 00:42:30,260
What a coincidence.

800
00:42:31,130 --> 00:42:32,660
What are you so happy about?

801
00:42:33,340 --> 00:42:34,630
Happy? Not at all.

802
00:42:35,870 --> 00:42:37,130
Then why did you drink?

803
00:42:37,300 --> 00:42:38,420
It's only 8:30.

804
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:41,360
You're usually still working at this hour.

805
00:42:41,460 --> 00:42:42,670
Is there some wonderful news

806
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:43,560
you're celebrating?

807
00:42:43,560 --> 00:42:45,840
Who says drinking is
only for celebrations?

808
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:47,460
Can't I drink to drown my sorrows?

809
00:42:47,460 --> 00:42:50,150
You're so concerned
about the party and country.

810
00:42:50,150 --> 00:42:51,270
I'm deeply impressed!

